                "interventionModel": "PARALLEL",
                "interventionModelDescription": "The patients will be randomized into one of two groups, either continuous antibiotic usage until the EVD is removed or antibiotics for a total of twenty-four hours; in both cases antibiotics will begin no more than sixty minutes pre-procedure.",
                "primaryPurpose": "OTHER",
